  "description": "Find out whether your biometric data is likely to be on a police database -  fingerprints, DNA sample, kept after arrest, crime, conviction",
  "details": {
    "body": "<p>Find out whether your biometric data is likely to be on a police database.</p>\n\n<p>Police will usually take some of your biometric data if you’re arrested, including your fingerprints and DNA. This data may then be stored in a police database, depending on the crime and whether or not you were convicted.</p>\n",
