      },
      {
        "body": "<p>You can withdraw your consent at any time by writing to the police force that took your data.</p>\n",
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-1",
        "title": "Your DNA sample or fingerprints will not be stored on any national databases unless you’ve given written consent."
      },
      {
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-2",
        "title": "Your DNA sample and fingerprints will be kept indefinitely."
      },
      {
        "body": "<p>After 3 years, the police may apply to a District Judge to keep your data for a further 2 years.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"find-out-whether-your-dna-sample-and-fingerprint-records-have-already-been-deleted\">Find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprint records have already been deleted</h3>\n\n<p>You can make a <a href=\"/copy-of-police-records\">‘subject access request’</a> to the police force that arrested you to find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprints are being held, or whether they have already been destroyed or deleted.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"apply-to-get-biometrics-deleted\">Apply to get biometrics deleted</h3>\n\n<p>You can apply to the Chief Officer of Police of the police force that arrested you to have your DNA sample and fingerprint records deleted or destroyed. They may ask you further questions before they make a decision.</p>\n",
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-3",
        "title": "Your fingerprints and DNA sample will be kept for 3 years. "
      },
      {
        "body": "<p>Your fingerprints and DNA sample will be kept for 3 years if a Chief Officer of Police makes an application to the <a href=\"/government/organisations/biometrics-commissioner/about\">Biometrics Commissioner</a> for permission.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"find-out-whether-your-dna-sample-and-fingerprint-records-have-already-been-deleted\">Find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprint records have already been deleted</h3>\n\n<p>You can make a <a href=\"/copy-of-police-records\">‘subject access request’</a> to the police force that arrested you to find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprints are being held, or whether they have already been destroyed or deleted.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"how-to-apply-to-get-biometrics-deleted\">How to apply to get biometrics deleted</h3>\n\n<p>You can apply to the Chief Officer of Police of the police force that arrested you to have your DNA sample and fingerprint records deleted or destroyed. They may ask you further questions before they make a decision.</p>\n",
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-4",
        "title": "Your fingerprints and DNA sample may be kept for 3 years."
      },
      {
        "body": "<h3 id=\"find-out-whether-your-dna-sample-and-fingerprint-records-have-already-been-deleted\">Find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprint records have already been deleted</h3>\n\n<p>You can make a <a href=\"/copy-of-police-records\">‘subject access request’</a> to the police force that arrested you to find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprints are being held, or whether they have already been destroyed or deleted.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"how-to-apply-to-get-biometrics-deleted\">How to apply to get biometrics deleted</h3>\n\n<p>You can apply to the Chief Officer of Police of the police force that arrested you to have your DNA sample and fingerprint records deleted or destroyed. They may ask you further questions before they make a decision.</p>\n",
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-5",
        "title": "Your fingerprints and DNA sample may be kept for 2 years."
      },
      {
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-6",
        "title": "Your fingerprints and DNA sample will not be kept but will be checked to see if they match with any crime scene records stored in databases."
      },
      {
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-7",
        "title": "Your fingerprints and DNA sample may be kept for the length of your sentence plus 5 years."
      },
      {
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-8",
        "title": "Your fingerprints and DNA sample may be kept for 5 years from the date the fingerprints were taken or the DNA sample was derived."
      },
      {
        "body": "<p>After 3 years, the police may apply to a District Judge to keep your data for a further 2 years.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"find-out-whether-your-dna-sample-and-fingerprint-records-have-already-been-deleted\">Find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprint records have already been deleted</h3>\n\n<p>Your parent or guardian can make a <a href=\"/copy-of-police-records\">‘subject access request’</a> to the police force that arrested you to find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprints are being held, or whether they have already been destroyed or deleted.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"apply-to-get-biometrics-deleted\">Apply to get biometrics deleted</h3>\n\n<p>You can apply to the Chief Officer of Police of the police force that arrested you to have your DNA sample and fingerprint records deleted or destroyed. They may ask you further questions before they make a decision.</p>\n\n",
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-9",
        "title": "Your fingerprints and DNA sample may be kept for 3 years. "
      },
      {
        "body": "<p>Your fingerprints and DNA sample will be kept for 3 years if a Chief Officer of Police makes an application to the <a href=\"/government/organisations/biometrics-commissioner/about\">Biometrics Commissioner</a> for permission. After 3 years, the police may then apply to a District Judge to keep your data for a further 2 years.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"find-out-whether-your-dna-sample-and-fingerprint-records-have-already-been-deleted\">Find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprint records have already been deleted</h3>\n\n<p>Your parent or guardian can make a <a href=\"/copy-of-police-records\">‘subject access request’</a> to the police force that arrested you to find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprints are being held, or whether they have already been destroyed or deleted.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"how-to-apply-to-get-biometrics-deleted\">How to apply to get biometrics deleted</h3>\n\n<p>You can apply to the Chief Officer of Police of the police force that arrested you to have your DNA sample and fingerprint records deleted or destroyed. They may ask you further questions before they make a decision.</p>\n\n",
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-10",
        "title": "Your fingerprints and DNA sample may be kept for 3 years. "
      },
      {
        "body": "<h3 id=\"find-out-whether-your-dna-sample-and-fingerprint-records-have-already-been-deleted\">Find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprint records have already been deleted</h3>\n\n<p>Your parent or guardian can make a <a href=\"/copy-of-police-records\">‘subject access request’</a> to the police force that arrested you to find out whether your DNA sample and fingerprints are being held, or whether they have already been destroyed or deleted.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"how-to-apply-to-get-biometrics-deleted\">How to apply to get biometrics deleted</h3>\n\n<p>You can apply to the Chief Officer of Police of the police force that arrested you to have your DNA sample and fingerprint records deleted or destroyed. They may ask you further questions before they make a decision.</p>\n",
        "kind": "outcome",
        "options": [

        ],
        "slug": "outcome-11",
        "title": "Your fingerprints and DNA sample may be kept for 2 years."
      }
    ],
